---
import SectionTitle from "@src/components/elements/ui/SectionTitle.astro"
---

<div class="relative m-0 p-0">
  <div class="sticky top-0 -mt-[12vh] z-20 p-0 m-0"> 
    <div class="h-[20vh] w-full bg-[url('/WCUCC-Landing-Transition.svg')] bg-top bg-cover m-0 p-0"></div> 
  </div>

  <section class="relative z-40 bg-white p-5 sm:p-10 md:p-14 lg:p-20">
    <SectionTitle color="black">
      Our <br class="sm:hidden">Mission & Principles
    </SectionTitle>

    <p class="pb-2 lg:pb-10 text-2xl font-light">
      The 37th Western Canadian Undergraduate Chemistry Conference will be
      held at the University of British Columbia Okanagan, located in the
      Sylic Okanagan Territory, in May of 2025.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-4 pb-10">
      <p class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2 text-2xl font-light">
        This conference will provide undergraduates an opportunity to
        present their research, learn from luminaries in the field of
        chemistry, and connect with others to foster community. The guiding
        principles for this gathering are:
      </p>
      <div
        class="h-fit bg-white p-4 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300"
        style="border: 4px #000000 solid; border-radius: 0.5rem;"
      >
        <p
          class="w-fit rounded-lg p-2 text-lg"
          style="border: 1px #000000 solid; border-radius: 1rem;"
        >
          Diversity & Inclusion
        </p>
        <p class="py-10 text-5xl">Participants, Ideas, & Disciplines</p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="h-fit bg-white p-4 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 xl:mt-[-15rem]"
        style="border: 4px #000000 solid; border-radius: 0.5rem;"
      >
        <p
          class="w-fit rounded-lg p-2 text-lg"
          style="border: 1px #000000 solid; border-radius: 1rem;"
        >
          Interconnection
        </p>
        <p class="py-10 text-5xl">
          Across disciplines and students to build community
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="h-fit bg-white p-4 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 xl:mt-[-15rem]"
        style="border: 4px #000000 solid; border-radius: 0.5rem;"
      >
        <p
          class="w-fit rounded-lg p-2 text-lg"
          style="border: 1px #000000 solid; border-radius: 1rem;"
        >
          Application
        </p>
        <p class="py-10 text-5xl">
          Research findings to issues in the broader world
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="h-fit rounded-lg bg-white p-4 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300"
        style="border: 4px #000000 solid;"
      >
        <p
          class="w-fit rounded-lg p-2 text-lg"
          style="border: 1px #000000 solid; border-radius: 1rem;"
        >
          Accessibility
        </p>
        <p class="py-10 text-5xl">Information to Diverse Audiences</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="pb-10 text-2xl font-light">
      Our team looks forward to applying these principles in the planning and
      execution of what we hope will be a spectacular conference. We can't
      wait to welcome you to the beautiful Okanagan Valley.
    </p>
  </section>
</div>
